article_title: After Upgrades, Official Says 50,000 Can Now Use Obamacare Website Concurrently, 800,000 A Day

og.description: While acknowledging “more work to be done to continue to improve and enhance” the troubled healthcare.gov website, the Obama administration said upgrades and fixes to the online marketplace have allowed for “50,000 concurrent users” and 800,000 users a day.
